!!!
%html
    %head
        %title
            Rear Window 🕵️‍♀️
        %meta{charset: "utf-8"}
        %meta{name: "viewport", content:"width=device-width, initial-scale=1"}
        %link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,400i,700" rel="stylesheet")
        %link(rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css")
        %link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.8.2/css/bulma.min.css")
        %script(src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"   integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous")
        %script(src="/game_loby.js")
    %body{onload:"loby();"}
        .section.top-section
            .container
                .columns.is-centered
                    .column.is-8
                        %h1.title Rear Window Detective 🕵️‍♀️
                        %p.subtitle= "Game #{@game_description[:game].game_id}" 
                        %p In the classic film "Rear Window" L.B. Jefferies is confined to his home with an injured foot. His only source of entertainment was the world through his window. As a photographer, Jefferies was keen on observing the world through his window - and so shall we!
                        %br
                        #join{style: "display:none;"}
                            %h1.title Join This Game 👇
                            %form.field.is-grouped#join-game
                                %input#join-game-id{type: "text", name: "game", value: "#{@game_description[:game].game_id}", style: "display:none;" }
                                .control.is-expanded
                                    %input.input.is-large#join-game-name{type: "text", name: "username", required: true, placeholder: "Name" }
                                .control
                                    %button.button.is-primary.is-large#join-game-button{ type: 'submit', value: "Join" }
                                        Join 
                        #start{style: "display:none;",  onload:"joinOrStart()"}
                            %button.button.is-primary.is-large#begin-game-button{ type: 'submit', value: "Start the Game!" }
                                Start the Game 🏁 
                                   
        .section{style: "background-color:white"}
            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-8
                        %h2.title Players 🎭
                        - @game_description[:players].each do |player|
                            .content.is-medium!= "Player <em>#{player.name}</em> #{["💪", "😎", "🧙‍♂️", "👩‍🎤", "👩‍🎨", "👩‍🚀", "👨‍🔬", "👩‍💻"].sample } joined"   
                    .column
                        %h2.title How To Play 📕
                        %p You'll be presented with images from around the world wide web. You'll be tasked with identifyig what's in those photos - but through emoji! You'll be givven a random pallete of 15 emoji - some are in the photo, some are not! The more you get right, the more points you get. The more you get wrong, the more points you loose. Sit back and enjoy until the game begins!


